<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="fgets" id="fgets">fgets</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdio&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span><span class="kw3">fgets</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str, <span class="kw4">int</span> num, <span class="kw4">FILE</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>stream <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

fgets()从文件流中读取至多  num - 1 个字符并存储在str中。由fgets()得到的字符串始终是NULL结尾的。fgets()在到达行尾时停止，这种情况下str将包含换行字符。否则，fgets()将在到达 num - 1 个字符或者遇到EOF字符时停止。成功时fgets()返回str，错误时返回NULL。
</p>

<p>
相关主题： <a href="fputs" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:fputs">fputs</a>, <a href="fscanf" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:fscanf">fscanf</a>, <a href="gets" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:gets">gets</a>, <a href="scanf" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:scanf">scanf</a>
</p>

